{"tid":1266764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首個 AI 宇宙模擬器面世，效果令人驚訝","createTime":"2019-06-29T15:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T10:06:21.000Z","uid":22675,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0b3bb9fe40f0838a29bbb4c527fe8e64b7a0dc40","tid":1266764,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:34:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.pro/2019/06/27/first-ai-simulating-universe/ai/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.pro%2F2019%2F06%2F27%2Ffirst-ai-simulating-universe%2Fai%2F&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo7XdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=9aec78a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.pro/2019/06/27/first-ai-simulating-universe/ai/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/13195108/space-universe-galaxy-star-2-768x432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F13195108%2Fspace-universe-galaxy-star-2-768x432.jpg&h=55baf6d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人工智慧（AI）可做複雜運算，天文學家也認為宇宙運作有一定規律，因此人工智慧宇宙模擬器就應運而生。最近有科學家製作了首個 AI 宇宙模擬器，且效果非常理想，相信未來可帶來更大的研究價值。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一批科學家利用深度神經網路 Deep Density Displacement Model（D3M），預測宇宙結構形成，比起傳統運算，人工智慧技術可提供更快速的分析，且成果遠超過原始數據。研究人員表示，AI 模擬器的成果竟然超過原先輸入的訓練數據，他們只是輸入不同的黑暗物質數值，但系統自動基於未知的原因改變數值。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（Source：論文）<br />\n<br />\n研究人員分享，這就像只訓練圖像分析系統辨認貓和狗，但忽然 AI 可辨認大象，這現象目前仍無法解釋。模擬器除了能進一步展示黑盒 AI 和深度學習的不可預測性質，還有可能幫助天體物理學家和研究人員了解宇宙未知的那面。"},{"pid":"d4a96c6e6c341e3ce35bc1618b6af96e04c8f81b","tid":1266764,"uid":237096,"like":3,"dislike":25,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:36:54.000Z","msg":"反送中，無時間理呢D，不了"},{"pid":"32897d968513350f14c378c47526e168be9eee2a","tid":1266764,"uid":22675,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"d4a96c6e6c341e3ce35bc1618b6af96e04c8f81b","tid":1266764,"uid":237096,"like":3,"dislike":25,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:36:54.000Z","msg":"反送中，無時間理呢D，不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"近排多負能量啊，睇下呢啲散下心"},{"pid":"f30a7770f748e1be08f4f3aa37920088f35be5f6","tid":1266764,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:39:10.000Z","msg":"我哋依家個世界都可能係電腦模擬出嚟,就好似sims咁"},{"pid":"7c45d8c632b7aad72b4d73e4653b1fc14d990ace","tid":1266764,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T15:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36977ee46cfaf6c14ff4816f81b1d8842c09670c","tid":1266764,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:26:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4098325ccf05e9e946e08f66f90d8f20ee0ecd4","tid":1266764,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:11:01.000Z","msg":"當呢類技術愈嚟愈勁嘅時候, 啲人就會開始諗：究竟自己身處緊嘅宇宙係咪都係模擬出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7bf03764030b2c0d814abf76c4a40bacb82811","tid":1266764,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:18:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20baa87180540fa94fa11d1295e007e955adf810","tid":1266764,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:19:06.000Z","msg":"笑左 又多個平行宇宙"},{"pid":"1a30a2d1dc579e40c82ffc2b9751195e712a4e30","tid":1266764,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:22:16.000Z","msg":"有研究指時間只係人類錯覺，過去現在未來同時存在。<br />\n<br />\n呢部電腦可能運算到呢個龐大存在"},{"pid":"945197db5a57a83131794ede3d788b19fd896500","tid":1266764,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T23:50:47.000Z","msg":"有人推斷呢個世界係虛擬，就係全部都可以用數據砌出黎，就如我地整隻game一樣，諗下呢個世界都係俾數字支配住"},{"pid":"a7f4a40c1b46eb988cc23da66b44018fc65610bb","tid":1266764,"uid":19868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T00:00:20.000Z","msg":"Source : 論文 <img src=\"